âš™ï¸ 2. Installing Kind
Kind supports multiple installation methods:

ğŸ”§ Method	ğŸ–¥ï¸ Platform	ğŸ“œ Command
ğŸ macOS	Brew	brew install kind
ğŸªŸ Windows	Choco / Scoop	choco install kind
